<!-- CASE STUDY -->
<section class="case"><div class="ctr">
<div class="badge">CLIENT CASE STUDY</div>
<h2 class="sec-h2">3,000+ SKUs in one warehouse: how we organised storage</h2>
<div class="case-inner">
<div class="case-text">
<p>An accessories online store came to MTP Group with a problem: 3,200 product lines were stored in a garage, inventory counts took 3 days, and order errors reached 8% due to mix-ups.</p>
<blockquote>&laquo;We were losing 40,000 UAH per month on wrong shipments and returns. After moving to the MTP warehouse, the first inventory count showed a discrepancy of just 0.3%&raquo;</blockquote>
<p><strong>MTP solution:</strong> each of the 3,200 products was assigned a unique bin with an address in the WMS. Barcode scanning at every stage &mdash; from receiving to dispatch. Result: order accuracy rose from 92% to 99.7%, and inventory counts now take 4 hours instead of 3 days.</p>
</div>
